Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    com.tapjoy.Tapjoy.showOffers()
    Deprecated since version 11.0.0. Tapjoy Offerwall should now be configured through TJPlacement Show available offers to the user
    com.tapjoy.Tapjoy.showOffers(TJOffersListener)
    Deprecated since version 11.0.0. Tapjoy Offerwall should now be configured through TJPlacement Show available offers to the user. Data is returned to the callback TJOffersListener
    com.tapjoy.Tapjoy.showOffersWithCurrencyID(String, boolean)
    Deprecated since version 11.0.0. Tapjoy Offerwall should now be configured through TJPlacement Show available offers using a currencyID and currency selector flag. This should only be used if the application supports multiple currencies and is NON-MANAGED by Tapjoy.
    com.tapjoy.Tapjoy.showOffersWithCurrencyID(String, boolean, TJOffersListener)
    Deprecated since version 11.0.0. Tapjoy Offerwall should now be configured through TJPlacement Show available offers using a currencyID and currency selector flag. This should only be used if the application supports multiple currencies and is NON-MANAGED by Tapjoy. Data is returned to the callback TJOffersListener.
